```json
{
	"_data": {
		"_scalar": {
			"_class": "_class_quantity",
			"_type": "_type_integer",
			"_min-range-inclusive": 5,
			"_max-range-inclusive": 10
		}
	}
}
```

This example describes a *scalar discrete integer* quantitative value in the range from `5` to `10` inclusive.

